Handy utilities

  make installdeps
  make test
  make install # check the paths in the Makefile first!

these require perl and install to your /home

it's strongly suggested to configure cpanm and local::lib first

the code tends to require perl 5.14.  Perl::MinimumVersion can be used to
check compatibility.

code quality was reviewed with `perlcritic --theme freenode`.
